From b31eec5bf7d443ae502c0ae42446483e666ef36a Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: GW2 WvW Log System <gw2-log-system@example.com>
Date: Sat, 9 May 2026 01:44:09 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] fix: add missing build module files ignored by .gitignore

The frontend/.gitignore had 'build/' which incorrectly ignored source
directories like src/api/build/, src/services/build/, src/store/build/.
Changed to '/build/' to only ignore root-level build output.

Also includes the build module source files required for compilation.
